en.learn:
**Command:** %p%learn
**Description:** 'Teaches' the bot a new command, this command can be used by any member thereon, can output anything you wish.
Optional Arguments:
**%cd #%**, cooldown for the command in seconds;
**%admin**, staff only command;
**%me**, will be replaced with the person who did the command's mention;
**%user**, will be replaced with the first mentioned user;
**%message**, will be replaced by the entirety of the message the person sends.
**Usage:** %p%learn [command name] [response]
**Example:** !learn biteme Hell no that's unsanitary.
